headline: Three Stocks Flash Triple Strengths; A Data Center Play Is One Of Them
summary: Three stocks were flashing strength to end a week of volatile trades in Friday's stock market.  All three now are scaling new records as they hover in buy zones with relative strength lines at 52-week highs.  GE Aerospace is in a buy zone above an entry at 332.79 as shares also hit an all-time high.
